### Daily Us API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@email = sample-email
@password = Password1!
@nickname = tester
@accessToken = access-token
@refreshToken = refresh-token

### 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "nickname": "{{nickname}}"
}

### 로그인
# @name signin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}

### 토큰 재발급
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 유저 팔로우
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/2/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 유저 언팔로우
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/2/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 게시물 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "imageUrls": [
    "https://cdn.example.com/posts/1.png",
    "https://cdn.example.com/posts/2.png"
  ],
  "content": "오늘 기록 #Morning #Routine"
}

### 피드 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/posts?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 로그아웃
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
